#. UnifiedRole Editor, Role Description (resolves directly)
#. UnifiedRole SpaceEditorWithoutVersionsWithoutTrashbin, Role Description
#. (resolves directly)
#: pkg/unifiedrole/roles.go:150 pkg/unifiedrole/roles.go:226
