msgstr "ເບິ່ງ, ດາວໂຫຼດ, ອັບໂຫຼດ, ແກ້ໄຂ, ເພີ່ມ ແລະ ລຶບ."

#. UnifiedRole SpaceEditorWithoutTrashbin, Role Description (resolves
#. directly)
#: pkg/unifiedrole/roles.go:218
