#. UnifiedRole SpaceEditorWithoutVersions, Role Description (resolves
#. directly)
#: pkg/unifiedrole/roles.go:210
msgid "View, download, upload, edit, add, delete and restore from trash bin."
msgstr ""

#. UnifiedRole EditorListGrants Editor, Role Description (resolves directly)
#: pkg/unifiedrole/roles.go:158
msgid "View, download, upload, edit, add, delete and show all invited people."
msgstr ""
"ເບິ່ງ, ດາວໂຫຼດ, ອັບໂຫຼດ, ແກ້ໄຂ, ເພີ່ມ, ລຶບ ແລະ ສະແດງລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຖືກເຊີນທັງໝົດ."

#. UnifiedRole SpaceEditor, Role Description (resolves directly)
#: pkg/unifiedrole/roles.go:234
msgid ""
"View, download, upload, edit, add, delete, show all versions and restore "
"from trash bin."
msgstr ""

#. UnifiedRole Manager, Role Description (resolves directly)
#: pkg/unifiedrole/roles.go:242
msgid ""
"View, download, upload, edit, add, delete, show all versions, restore from "
"trash bin, empty the trash bin and manage members."
msgstr ""

#. UnifiedRole EditorListGrantsWithVersions, Role Description (resolves
#. directly)
#: pkg/unifiedrole/roles.go:166
msgid ""
"View, download, upload, edit, delete, show all versions and all invited "
"people."
msgstr ""
"ເບິ່ງ, ດາວໂຫຼດ, ອັບໂຫຼດ, ແກ້ໄຂ, ລຶບ, ສະແດງເວີຊັນທັງໝົດ ແລະ "
"ສະແດງລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຖືກເຊີນທັງໝົດ."

#. UnifiedRole FileEditorListGrantsWithVersions, Role Description (resolves
#. directly)
